¶ ¶

39:26.932 --> 39:29.499
(sighs)

39:29.501 --> 39:33.103
(gasps)
Who's there?

39:33.105 --> 39:35.038
Christophe.

39:35.040 --> 39:37.774
You are supposed
to be in Chambord.

39:37.776 --> 39:39.542
I'm afraid it didn't suit me.

39:39.544 --> 39:40.877
I kept straying from my post.

39:40.879 --> 39:42.779
What? To kill?

39:42.781 --> 39:46.015
I'm worse away from you,
Catherine. I truly am.

39:46.017 --> 39:50.153
(horn blowing)

