¶ Take me down
by the altar... ¶

40:02.701 --> 40:03.967
What is that?

40:03.969 --> 40:04.968
The Red Knights.

40:04.970 --> 40:06.703
(man grunts)

40:06.705 --> 40:08.505
Catherine, watch out!

40:09.040 --> 40:10.874
(horn blowing)

